Class TreeSet<T>

java.lang.Object
  ds.util.TreeSet<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements held in this collection
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collection<T>, OrderedSet<T>, Set<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
public class TreeSet<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements OrderedSet<T>, Iterable<T>

An implementation of the OrderedSet using STNode elements and binary search tree (STree algorithms.
